      "description": "Exceptionally clean, beautifully kept mint-condition example that shows just how well it has been cared for. The paint, interior, and overall presentation are standout, and it has the sharp, well-preserved look buyers hope to find in a top-tier car. A truly impressive vehicle that\u2019s ready to enjoy.",
