      "description": "Used car in fair condition. It runs and drives, but it shows clear wear from age and use and will likely need some maintenance or repairs over time. The interior and exterior are presentable but have noticeable cosmetic imperfections. A reasonable choice for someone looking for basic transportation at a lower price point.",
