    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "A budget-friendly opportunity for the right buyer, this vehicle offers straightforward value with solid potential as an inexpensive daily driver, project, or backup car. It shows its age and is best suited for someone who appreciates a practical purchase at an accessible price point. If you\u2019re looking for affordable transportation without unnecessary hype, this is a chance to buy from a trusted seller at a price that makes sense.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "If you\u2019re after an affordable set of wheels with plenty of character, this one could be a great fit. It\u2019s not a showroom car, but it starts, runs, and offers a straightforward, budget-friendly way to get on the road. A sensible option for someone who doesn\u2019t mind a bit of cosmetic wear and wants honest value without spending a fortune. Priced fairly and ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 6800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly project or workhorse with a strong-running engine, dependable transmission engagement, and a chassis that still feels like it has plenty of life left in it. Shows its age cosmetically and will want some TLC, but it starts, moves, and offers a great foundation for someone who knows their way around basic maintenance. Simple, proven mechanicals make this an ideal fixer-upper, commuter beater, or parts donor with real usable value left. Priced to move for someone looking for affordable transportation with upside.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car. Rough around the edges, priced to move fast. First serious buyer takes it.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of presence that turns a simple drive into a little adventure. It\u2019s not pretending to be perfect\u2014that\u2019s part of its charm. With a seasoned look and a story in every panel, it offers an honest, no-frills driving experience for someone who appreciates character over polish. Whether you need an affordable runabout, a practical project, or a dependable spare to keep life moving, this one brings real-world usefulness and plenty of potential. A budget-friendly opportunity to own something with personality and purpose.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
